# 2026 Web Infrastructure Optimization Checklist

## 1. Performance
- [ ] Edge Caching Strategy implemented?
- [ ] Image optimization (AVIF/WebP)?
- [ ] Font sub-setting and optimization?

## 2. Scalability
- [ ] Database connection pooling enabled?
- [ ] Serverless function timeouts configured?
- [ ] Horizontal auto-scaling set up?

## 3. SEO
- [ ] Dynamic sitemap generation?
- [ ] Structured data (JSON-LD) for all content types?
- [ ] Canonical tags properly set?

## 4. Automation
- [ ] Automated CI/CD pipeline?
- [ ] Error tracking (Sentry/LogRocket)?
- [ ] Automated backup verification?

